From: Przemek Kitszel <przemyslaw.kitszel@intel.com>
Date: Mon, 16 Dec 2024 15:15:31 +0100
Subject: devlink: add devlink_fmsg_put() macro
Patch-mainline: v6.14-rc1
Git-commit: 346947223bacf96155f603528823a60b18b92d9a
References: jsc#PED-10419

Add devlink_fmsg_put() that dispatches based on the type
of the value to put, example: bool -> devlink_fmsg_bool_pair_put().

